      "writtenOn": "2021-03-02T02:57:54Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This is what project-scoped service accounts is meant to do; I don\u0027t think we should replicate that effort here.\n\nSince it looks like some projects STILL don\u0027t have project scoped accounts, however, I think we can set a boolean here `use_insecure_global_logdog_account`. If `true`, it will use `logdog@`, otherwise will use the project-configured -scoped account.\n\ntandrii, wdyt?",
